### Shared actors
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/demo/actors

### Donor dashboard
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/donor/me/dashboard
X-Actor-Id: 101

### Create mock payment
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/donor/payments
Content-Type: application/json
X-Actor-Id: 101

{
  "amountKrw": 50000
}

### Convert the newly created payment
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/donor/payments/6002/convert
X-Actor-Id: 101

### Create donation allocation
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/donor/allocations
Content-Type: application/json
X-Actor-Id: 101

{
  "charityId": 1001,
  "points": 10000
}

### Charity manager allocations
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/charity/me/allocations
X-Actor-Id: 201

### Charity manager creates partner order from one allocation
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/charity/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-Actor-Id: 201

{
  "allocationId": 9003,
  "partnerProductId": 2001,
  "quantity": 1
}

### Admin orders queue
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/orders
X-Actor-Id: 301

### Admin completes a partner order
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/orders/10002/complete
X-Actor-Id: 301

### Allocation detail timeline
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/allocations/9003/detail
